<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-34-0785 </DOCNO><TEXT>A description of the bread baking process is given as well as an overviewof current oven types (gas-fueled and electrical). Data are presentedon the energy consumption of ovens and on energy losses. An indicationis given of which losses are suitable for recovery and re-usage. Finallysome recommendations for further research are noted, which can contributeto lowering the energy consumption or energy recovery from bread bakeryovens. 8 figs., 11 refs., 3 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>